---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

---

<Layout title="Disclaimer" description="Disclaimer for Chirag Singhal's Digital Identity">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-[var(--content-max-width)] px-6 py-12">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal-500/10 border border-teal-500/20 text-xs text-teal-300/80 mb-6">
        <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal-400 animate-pulse"></span>
        Legal
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-3" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/40 max-w-2xl">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="space-y-10 text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">1. General Information</h2>
        <p>The information contained on this website is for general information purposes only. While we endeavor to keep the information up to date and correct, we make no representations or warranties of any kind, express or implied, about the completeness, accuracy, reliability, suitability, or availability with respect to the website.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">2. External Links</h2>
        <p>Through this website, you are able to link to other websites which are not under our control. We have no control over the nature, content, and availability of those sites. The inclusion of any links does not necessarily imply a recommendation or endorse the views expressed within them.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">3. AI Generated Content</h2>
        <p>This website utilizes artificial intelligence tools to interact and generate content (e.g., chat agent). Any outputs, answers, or code suggested by the AI are provided "as is" and should be reviewed thoroughly before any real-world application. We take no responsibility for errors, hallucinations, or damages arising from AI-generated answers.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">4. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Questions about this disclaimer should be directed to: <a href="mailto:hi@chirag127.in" class="text-teal-400 hover:text-teal-300 hover:underline ml-1 transition-colors">hi@chirag127.in</a></p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
